                      <span>2004-06-24</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>I've read both Blowback and The Sorrows of Empire. Chalmers Johnson is a brilliant political scientiest. He loves his country, but he wants to see change. Hopefully America heeds the lessons of this powerful book.</span>
                  
              
